extensionMeta.name: Layout container
extensionMeta.description: The layout container object has a canvas that can hold multiple objects. In this container you can freely move objects around, as well as position the objects on top of each other or overlapping.

bundle.name: Qlik Dashboard bundle
bundle.description:
This is a set of supported objects that will facilitate dashboard creation in Qlik Sense. These can be used in addition to the objects found under "Charts".

For limitations and support conditions, see the documentation.

qDef.qDef:
({<REPORT_PERIOD_COST_DATE={'$(=$(v.Cost_time_selector_partial_period))'}>} [Total cost / credits] - ({<REPORT_PERIOD_COST_DATE={'$(=$(v.Costs_comparator1))'}>}[Total cost / credits]))
/
({<REPORT_PERIOD_COST_DATE={'$(=$(v.Costs_comparator1))'}>}[Total cost / credits])

((sum({<REPORT_PERIOD_COST_DATE={'$(=$(v.Cost_time_selector_partial_period))'}>} COST) 
	/ 
	Count({<REPORT_PERIOD_COST_DATE={'$(=$(v.Cost_time_selector_partial_period))'}>} DISTINCT COST_DATE)) 
	* Count({<REPORT_PERIOD_COST_DATE={$(v.Cost_current_date)}>} DISTINCT COST_DATE))
/
(sum({<REPORT_PERIOD_COST_DATE={'Today'}>} CONTRACT_AMOUNT) / $(v.Cost_ProRata_contract))
